                <head>Comments</head>
                <p xml:id="KR2a0007-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_000-1a.1-h" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2022-08-26T21:21:21.013+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_014-7a.62" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-06T00:28:13.384+09:00">What the Han obtained is formal/ritual CONTROL OVER the feudal states. But the question is whether 得 itself may not have to be taken to mean "gain formal/ritual control of". Xu Jialu 2014 tr.: 因此漢得到天 下以來，常想治理得很好，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_055-14a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-09-15T16:13:43.944+09:00">許嘉璐：＇孔子説：＇我想與其用空洞的説教去教育別人，還不如記載具體歷史事件，因事見義，更爲深切顯明。  張烈2755: ，孔子说”｀我想要另立空洞的说教，不如就在位者所行之事进行深刻剖析而使道理更加明白。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_069-46a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T19:13:50.789+09:00">When the time is right to remain inactive then remain inactive;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_069-46a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T19:14:32.358+09:00">when the time is right to act then proceed to take action.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_101-21a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-20T00:38:34.763+09:00">Very fundamentally</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_101-21a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-20T00:38:47.28+09:00">counting starts with the number one.</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
